OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'My energy firm forced me  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fonto a prepayment meter'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Citizens Advice has called for a ban on
OL,6, energy companies "forcing" customers   
OL,7, onto prepayment meters because they are
OL,8, struggling to pay bills.               
OL,10,FThe charity estimates that 3.2 million 
OL,11,Fpeople in Britain ran out of credit on 
OL,12,Ftheir prepayment meter last year, the  
OL,13,Fequivalent of one every 10 seconds.    
OL,15,FAudrey Ridson, 81, was switched to one 
OL,16,Feven though she could not walk to the  
OL,17,Fshop to top up her energy card.        
OL,19,FMinisters said that energy firms must  
OL,20,Foffer help to those struggling.        
